<https://globular.io/awareness#decision/decision.dashboard_v1_read_only_over_grpc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Agents and humans want to act on what the dashboard shows, but there is no guarded backend mutation API yet, so any UI write path would bypass review." .
<https://globular.io/awareness#decision/decision.dashboard_v1_read_only_over_grpc> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Promotion remains a CLI step; the dashboard stays a pure read surface." .
