<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.infer_question_state_next_action_closure_or_lifecycle_in_the> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://globular.io/awareness#ForbiddenFix> .
<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.infer_question_state_next_action_closure_or_lifecycle_in_the> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The inspector must render artifact_state fields verbatim; questions/evidence/next-action are owner ids with no state, and closure/lifecycle/severity come from the owner. Any client inference fabricates architectural truth." .
<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.infer_question_state_next_action_closure_or_lifecycle_in_the> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Infer question-state next-action closure or lifecycle in the inspector" .
