<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.infer_question_state_next_action_closure_or_lifecycle_in_the> <https://globular.io/awareness#authoredIn> "docs/awareness/forbidden_fixes.yaml" .
<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.map_an_absent_optional_count_to_zero> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://globular.io/awareness#ForbiddenFix> .
<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.map_an_absent_optional_count_to_zero> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "proto3 optional counts decode to undefined when unobserved; rendering absence as 0 (e.g. Number(x||0)) launders unknown state into a false healthy zero. Presence must be read via the synthetic-oneof marker." .
<https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenFix/forbidden_fix.sensei.map_an_absent_optional_count_to_zero> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Map an absent optional count to zero" .
