<https://globular.io/awareness#implementationPattern/implementation_pattern.awg_dashboard_read_only> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A UI that reads backend authority over a narrow read-only contract cannot become a hidden writer; mutation stays on the guarded CLI/backend path." .
