<https://globular.io/awareness#implementationPattern/implementation_pattern.collect_impact_scope_resolver> <https://globular.io/awareness#activationTrigger> "building impact or briefing results that span repos/domains" .
<https://globular.io/awareness#implementationPattern/implementation_pattern.collect_impact_scope_resolver> <https://globular.io/awareness#activationTrigger> "loading knowledge that must be constrained to a resolved scope" .
