<https://globular.io/awareness#implementationPattern/implementation_pattern.collect_impact_scope_resolver> <https://globular.io/awareness#forbiddenShortcut> "Treating an untagged node as belonging to every domain." .
<https://globular.io/awareness#implementationPattern/implementation_pattern.collect_impact_scope_resolver> <https://globular.io/awareness#implementsDecision> <https://globular.io/awareness#decision/decision.untagged_domain_defaults_home> .
